We’re thrilled to announce that we’ve reached 10k followers today!🎉

Our mission is to provide access to accurate testing for SIBO, IMO, ISO, IBS, and Malabsorption. We couldn't achieve this without the incredible support of practitioners and patients who trust and use our products every day. Thank you for your unwavering trust and valuable feedback! Your support motivates us to keep advancing our research to improve the lives of those facing these challenging conditions. We are committed to delivering the best testing options, top-notch customer service, and valuable educational information to support your health journey.

Here’s to growing together, and continuing to make a positive impact on gut health! 💜💖💚
